ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_1: You are only a bearer of warnings.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_2: You are no more than a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_4: You are purely a Herald of Warning.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_6: You are naught but a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_7: thou art naught but a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_10: Thou art naught but a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_12: Thou art no other than a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_13: You (O Muhammad SAW) are only a warner (i.e. your duty is to convey Allah's Message to mankind but the guidance is in Allah's Hand).
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_14: You (Prophet Muhammad) are but a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_16: You, [O Muhammad], are not but a warner.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_17: [35:23] You are but a warner, to them.
ENGLISH.TRANSLATION_18: (Thou) Muhammad (art but a warner) a Messenger warning by the Qur'an.
